title: Returned as a Martial Genius
description: Returned as a Martial Genius Manhwa It doesn’t matter how many times I wield a sword. I am talentless and a disgrace to my family, and could never accomplish anything. In the end, I simply died after the cataclysm occurred. … I thought I’d died, but I returned to seven years ago, with all my stats intact.
